commit message: Change directory structure to gradle conventions.
Read signing configuration from Gradle properties.
Describe gradle commands in build section.
Don't run test on device for now.
Move common code quality tools config to separate gradle file.
Allow to set lint abortOnError with a build property.
Add version suffix to apk name.
Use version 0.12.1 of android build tools.
New name of gradle android plugin.
Show build tag in about dialog.
Use https url for gradle wrapper.
